model

Class DBSchema

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.DBSchema

  • public class DBSchema
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is a model of relational database schema. It contains all the tables as well as the package structure which are described in the model.
    Author:
    Viktor, Jelena, Nikola
